relation: Darrow3 - #99 With Ness having recovered from his first kiss, the team prepares for their departure.
Darrow - #04 Don't ask why I chose a maple leaf design for that background, I have no idea where it came from. Also, Ness is finally outside so things actually start to happen. Yay!

Darrow - #40 If a man yells loud enough, he can do anything! The magic words to unleash a hero's true potential brings about the saving grace Ness needed. However, just channeling energy isn't enough, especially when you still don't have a cool attack name.
Darrow4 - #00 Saying farewell, the Sky Runner takes off with our three heroes into lands unknown. Well, actually, it's taking them to Summers. I guess that isn't really a spoiler, huh.
Darrow4 - #01 The Sky Runner crashes its last crash upon arriving at Summers, leaving only debris behind. Farewell, Sky Runner, we will miss you.
